      <p>Existing Web tools for the Luria-Delbrück fluctuation experiment do not offer many desirable capabilities that are vital to mutation research. webSalvador offers these capabilities via a user interface that allows researchers to access most of the functions in the R package rSalvador without having to learn the R language.</p>
